      <h3 class="divheading sm-above-large">Journey</h3>
      <p class="h5 l-1-5">From child prodigy to trail blazer, captivating audiences & critics, Dr.Manjunath has created an amazing record as Star performer in prestigious organizations world over.  From Royal Albert Hall in London to Sydney Opera House, from Common Thread Music festival in Oregon to Oxford University, from  Santa-Fe festival in New Mexico to World Music Festival in Chicago, from Esplanade Theatre in Singapore to Federation Squarein Melbourne, Dr.Manjunath has enthralled audiences all over the world.</p>
